      <h2>What to do</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Clean weekly with a mild liquid cleaner and soft sponge.</li>
        <li>Rinse thoroughly after each use.</li>
        <li>Wipe dry to prevent mineral buildup.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card" id="dont" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
      <h2>What to avoid</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Abrasive powders and scouring pads.</li>
        <li>Bleach, ammonia, and harsh drain cleaners.</li>
        <li>Suction-cup mats and organizers.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card" id="hard-water" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
      <h2>Hard-water tip for Pflugerville</h2>
      <p>Hard water can leave mineral spots quickly. A simple rinse and wipe after baths keeps the finish bright.</p>
